      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/global-funds-back-to-selling-chinese-stocks-as-optimism-fades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对经济和盈利放缓的担忧盖过了政策乐观情绪，外国投资者再次逃离中国股市，结束了持续四个月的资金流入热潮。]]></description>
